text: "Haute" is a song by American rapper Tyga. It was released on June 5, 2019 as the seventh single from his seventh album Legendary for streaming and digital download by Last Kings Music and Empire Distribution.https://music.apple.com/us/artist/haute/903027168 The song was produced by Dr. Luke and includes two guest verses from reggaeton singer J Balvin and longtime collaborator Chris Brown.
